mods.abstract: Three color window card (red and black on yellow) Hatch poster announcing the Duke of Paducah Show featuring George Morgan, Anita Carter, Kitty Wilson, Smiley Wilson, Lew Childre and Johnny Tona and Don Davis at the Carmichael Auditorium on May 10. Poster features metal photoplates of George Morgan, Anita Carter, Kitty Wilson, Smiley Wilson, Lew Childre and Johnny Tona and Don Davis.
